org.openscience.spectra

Class SimilarityRanker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openscience.spectra.SimilarityRanker

  • public class SimilarityRanker
extends java.lang.Object
    SimilarityRanker uses a SpectrumPredictor and parses an SDF file, returning a configurable number of compounds and their ranked spectrum similarity. This Open Source Software is provided to you under the MIT License Refer to doc/mit.license or https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT for more information Copyright (c) 2017, Christoph Steinbeck
